data.description: PRICE DROP! Located in the desirable area of Quartz Hill this home has a perfect floorplan for a large family.  The front yard is landscaped with green grass and and beautiful trees and plants. The backyard is extremely low maintenance, mostly cement grounds but has the space to entertain and BBQ. You'll be able to sit under the radiant sun or desert stars under the covered patio. Upon entering you'll walk into the first living room. Step further into the family room where you will find custom built-in entertainment cabinets, the kitchen has stainless steel appliances, newer wood look tile floors, a dining room and plenty of space to entertain. The primary bedroom is on the first floor and has a separate tub & shower, you'll have ample space with a double sink vanity, and a walk-in closet, and private toilet room. Another large bedroom on the opposite side of the house that is large enough for a mother in law's quarter or the perfect space for guests with a full bathroom nearby. The laundry room is large with lots of space and enters into the garage. Walk up the stairs and you find 2 more bedrooms with a jack and jill bathroom, a double vanity sink and a walk-in shower. You are in walking distance to one of the top schools.  Come look and let's get you into your new home.
